My apologies to Bill's Punch Line, but I prefer the more optomistic =
side. What do you think of mine?

What happens when you fall in love with:

A chef? (Cooks up a good life for you)

A chauffeur? (Takes you for the ride of your life)

A gambler? (Beats all the odds for relationship longevity.)

A telephone operator? (Makes the best connection for you.)

A trashman? (Keeps the relationship clean.)

A clockmaker?  (Always makes time for you.)

A pastry cook? (Always so sweet.)

A shoe salesman?  (Fits you to a "T" and makes a relationship that =
lasts- pun intended.)

An elevator operator? (Makes the ride of life bearable.)

An artist? (Always paints the rosiest picture of any situation.)

A jogger? (Pushes you to be your best.)


I'm sure I could think of more. My optomistic mind only took a few =
minute to come up with these.......

BCS


